 nbsp\; patron &nbsp\;of&nbsp\;TWiV! Links for this episode Support science
  education at MicrobeTV Positions in Rosenfeld Lab (email) Shingles vaccin
 ation may slow biological aging (J Gerontol) Getting virus classification 
 and nomenclature right (J Virol) Mucosal vaccination blocks diverse respir
 atory diseases (Science) Timestamps by&nbsp\; Jolene Ramsey. Thanks! Weekl
