UID:dead8db84bd4c316@gid-seminars.wnprc.wisc.edu
CATEGORIES:WHO
DESCRIPTION:World Health Day\, celebrated on 7 April 2026\, will kick off 
 a year-long campaign celebrating the power of scientific collaboration to 
 protect the health of people\, animals\, plants\, and the planet. The camp
 aign\, titled Together for health. Stand with science\, spotlights both sc
 ientific achievements and the multilateral cooperation needed to turn evid
 ence into action – through a strong focus on the One Health approach.\n\
 nEvent URL: https://www.who.int/news-room/events/detail/2026/04/07/default
 -calendar/world-health-day-2026-together-for-health-stand-with-science\n\n
